parameters: \nw[\N[3]]The Prope Forest... the location is here, right?

\nw[\N[3]]The desired material is... called Bakushou Kinoko,
huh? Just from the name, it feels poisonous.

\nw[\N[21]]She said it's for a tsukkomi, but what kind of
shop is a fuzoku ten anyway? Is a tsukkomi
necessary?

\nw[\N[3]]I've seen the second floor shop before. But I
thought it would be more like a tavern.

\nw[\N[21]]Hmmm... well, I'll ask about that later. For now,
let's confirm Uka's power.

\nw[\N[1]]It seems like there are monsters too, so let's
defeat them while searching.
\nw[\N[1]]Uka might be amazing... What do you two think?

\nw[\N[3]]I also think it's a good move. Even though she's
still young, she seems experienced.
\nw[\N[21]]Yeah, I feel like she's more capable than me.
\nw[\N[1]]Uka is fine, but... is it okay?

\nw[\N[1]]I thought \N[3] was trying to coordinate with us,
but it doesn't seem like that's the case...

\nw[\N[1]]Unlike us beginners, \N[3] was much stronger than
us. Yet her current actions are strange.

\nw[\N[1]]Haven't your injuries fully healed? If that's the
case, it might be better not to push yourself...

\nw[\N[3]]Um... Are you okay? Your injuries have already
healed, right?
\nw[\N[3]]......I've become unable to use magic very well.

\nw[\N[3]]I think I pushed myself a little too hard... so
maybe my soul got hurt.

\nw[\N[3]]Healing the soul is difficult even for high-level
magicians, so I think it would be challenging for
Prae-san as well. That's why I'm thinking of
waiting for natural recovery.

\nw[\N[3]]But don't worry, it's not like I've lost my
magical power. Just like body strengthening magic,
I can still use simple spells.

\nw[\N[1]]If you were hiding that, then maybe... no, it's
not just maybe.

\nw[\N[1]]It's because you got injured when you fought
against the Eaters, right?

\nw[\N[1]]I understand that \N[3] doesn't want to worry. So,
let's stop talking about this.

\nw[\N[1]]But if you have any troubles, please tell me. I...
we will support you.

\nw[\N[21]]This place is dirty. Someone said they'll clean it
later, so maybe it'll be usable someday.
